{"ts":"2026-06-10T10:33:45.487Z","author":"codex-impl","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-10T10:33:45.487Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments","value":[{"created_at":"2026-06-10T10:33:45.487Z","author":"codex-impl","text":"Mutation-surface specialist read-only pass: pm-xnkd close --duplicate-of, pm-p9hw create --parent fail-fast/default escape hatch, and pm-esf6 root --id-only are not implemented in current branch. close.ts/register-mutation.ts have no duplicateOf/--duplicate-of path; create.ts still uses settings.validation.parent_reference with default governance parent_reference=warn and tests assert warning behavior; global contracts/main/MCP/completions expose --no-changed-fields/fullChangedFields only, no --id-only. Expected follow-up surfaces: src/cli/commands/close.ts, src/cli/register-mutation.ts, src/cli/commands/create.ts, src/core/item/parent-reference-policy.ts, src/core/shared/constants.ts, src/cli/main.ts, src/sdk/cli-contracts.ts, src/mcp/server.ts, src/cli/commands/completion.ts, tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json, docs/COMMANDS.md, docs/AGENT_GUIDE.md, and focused unit/integration/MCP regressions."}]}],"before_hash":"b972ea370d6711c63c58724707136ae5a33b4c5149db6cd34b9cad4ca52b1d7b","after_hash":"b19d6e80ea639bd21004f186b939a295346d778b3dbfaa5cbd78a02010b4c1ef"}
{"ts":"2026-06-10T10:33:54.434Z","author":"codex-impl","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/1","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-10T10:33:54.434Z","author":"codex-impl","text":"Read-surface inspection: pm-awfr is implemented via DEFAULT_COMPACT_LIST_FIELDS including parent and has unit coverage. pm-ojpq is only partially present: hierarchy/progress completion-style stats exist, but high_level entries lack children_total/children_closed/completion_pct and recently_created/unparented sections are absent from section types, defaults, builders, and renderers. pm-eaer is not implemented: aggregate has no --completion option, no completion counters/pct fields, no registration/contracts/completion/docs/tests. No files edited by specialist."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-10T10:33:54.434Z"}],"before_hash":"b19d6e80ea639bd21004f186b939a295346d778b3dbfaa5cbd78a02010b4c1ef","after_hash":"16646c6622a0c6fdc38a8fd3183b3286bec5618270994093fd12b5b5d07ea5ab"}
