{"ts":"2026-06-10T10:46:38.613Z","author":"codex-impl","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/3","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-10T10:46:38.613Z","author":"codex-impl","text":"Evidence: implemented linked-test --add-json for complex command metadata, pm test --run selectors (--match/--only-index/--only-last) with selection metadata and background arg preservation, and aggregate --completion progress counters. Focused gates passed: tsc --noEmit; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/linked-test-parsers.spec.ts tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/unit/runtime-schema-command-flags.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/aggregate-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts; pnpm contracts:check. PM-owned linked tests passed after setting the contracts gate to tracker context. Manual temp-dir smoke passed for init/create/test --add-json/test --run --match/aggregate --completion with isolated PM_PATH and PM_GLOBAL_PATH. Wider gates passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (149 files, 2645 tests), pnpm quality:static, pnpm security:scan, pnpm audit --audit-level low, pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10, pm health --check-only --summary --json, pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift (history drift ok; pre-existing resolution metadata warnings remain)."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-10T10:46:38.613Z"}],"before_hash":"5741a9808971b6ee1c3d352d6f6826281e16dbbef91f83cafcfd9bd90b8ee670","after_hash":"2f260631bb02429e0bef745e39f43e9cfa05bda413eb2283886db9c712de88cc"}
{"ts":"2026-06-10T10:59:37.752Z","author":"codex-impl","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/4","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-10T10:59:37.752Z","author":"codex-impl","text":"Review response evidence: addressed Gemini review findings by using Object.hasOwn for --add-json key reads, rejecting empty numeric strings, requiring positive integer timeout_seconds, requiring --match/--only-index/--only-last to be paired with --run, and normalizing aggregate completion statuses against the runtime registry. Verification passed: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/linked-test-parsers.spec.ts tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/aggregate-command.spec.ts (92 tests); pnpm contracts:check; pnpm changelog:pm:check && pnpm contracts:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10; pnpm security:scan."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-10T10:59:37.752Z"}],"before_hash":"2f260631bb02429e0bef745e39f43e9cfa05bda413eb2283886db9c712de88cc","after_hash":"91a916c1f46b0cb11cabc3775a8921919daa885afb8a8ed54fd0c9e0552e588c"}
{"ts":"2026-06-10T11:08:46.556Z","author":"codex-impl","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/5","value":{"created_at":"2026-06-10T11:08:46.556Z","author":"codex-impl","text":"Review response evidence: addressed follow-up Gemini/CodeRabbit findings by preserving numeric onlyIndex values in command wiring, exposing pm test --list in bash/zsh/fish completions, exposing aggregate --completion in zsh completion, adding aggregate completion other counts for non-open/non-active/non-done statuses, and adding the aggregate completion action schema property. Verification passed: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/aggregate-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/unit/runtime-schema-command-flags.spec.ts tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/linked-test-parsers.spec.ts (208 tests); pnpm contracts:check; pnpm changelog:pm:check && pnpm contracts:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10; pnpm security:scan."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-06-10T11:08:46.556Z"}],"before_hash":"91a916c1f46b0cb11cabc3775a8921919daa885afb8a8ed54fd0c9e0552e588c","after_hash":"32a85f504c5d2efa5b9e091fb6dba19e4d27e6a5893829da99ef282328e8a224"}
